* We can create a swap partition or a swap file.

* To create a swap file 
- $ sudo fallocate -l 1G /swapfile      # make 1GB file
- $ sudo chmod 600 /swapfile           # set correct permission
- $ sudo mkswap /swapfile              # format as swap
- $ sudo swapon /swapfile              # turn it on

* To activate a swap partition we can use
- $ swapon /dev/sda1

* To deactivate the swap partition we can use
- $ swapoff /dev/sda1

